<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> left_reachable:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;exists-trace<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∃ </span>s0 s1 #i #j<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span>Secrets( s0, s1 ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #i<span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">∧</span> <span class="hl_operator">(</span>K( s0 ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span>&quot;<br/>
<a class="internal-link edit" href="/thy/trace/6/main/edit/left_reachable">edit lemma</a>  or  <a class="internal-link delete" href="/thy/trace/6/main/delete/left_reachable">delete lemma</a></span><br/>
